  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Runnable, java.util.EventListener, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, javax.swing.WindowConstants

    public class MainForm
extends javax.swing.JFrame
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.lang.Runnable
    GUI for running PBE_AESCipher. To create a jar file, choose: this java file (plus all java files from this package), its resources (java + image file), PBE_AESCipher from danfulea.crypto, Convertor.java from danfulea.math package, DanfuleaResources form danfulea.resources (images not needed), FrameUtilities, AboutFrame, LookAndFeel and ExampleFileFilter from danfulea.utils. As manifest choose the file from META-inf-MyWallet.
    Author:
    Dan Fulea, 29 MAR. 2010
    See Also:
